snippet.title: Ravenbound Official Announcement Trailer - Gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Fear everything and nothing for death brings you closer to victory in this challenging open world action-roguelite. Coming to PC via Steam. For more information and to join our beta, visit www.ravenboundgame.com


Follow Ravenbound on Social media: 
Twitter - https://twitter.com/RavenboundGame
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/RavenboundGame/
Discord - https://discord.gg/gTGtDsX3BE
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/ravenboundgame/
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@systemicreaction
